<author>C.Z.Huala</author>
<title>Kumsawt Kipahna In</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thihna luigal ah gam hawih nuom achun,
 Kumsawt van in zephawih chu a um;
 Lungtuok muolliem luipi kansate chun,
 Lui gal gam hawih achun ei ngak ui.

[V2]
 Kipahna In kumsawt nawpna mun chu,
 Kumkhuo'n mittui kiekna um talo;
 Hehpih Inkuon khat leh Hukdampa tawh,
 Hai loin kikhawpna um tana.

[V3]
 2. Ka kipak Lalpa, genchim thei puong ka,
 Kalvari zahhuoina cheng thuoka;
 Dogal hansie thuoka Na thih ziekin,
 Kei di'n kumsawt gam nuom Na siem tai.

[V4]
 3. Ka kahna leh ka buoina gamthip hi,
 Pelin zie thagau khawvel achun;
 Kalvari a Belam No thahsa kha,
 Lopina changin va mu tangka.</lyrics>
</song>